                        "text": "Group / Committee / forum which will receive the findings/monitoring report"
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Committee / individual responsible for ensuring the actions are completed"
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Applications to be reviewed by the recruitment department to ensure applications are completed correctly"
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Submission are emailed to mse.referafriend@nhs.net"
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Recruitment"
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Weekly"
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Will be reported directly to head of recruitment department"
                    },
                    {
                        "text": "Recruitment Managers"
