        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "text": "Appendix 1: Refer a friend scheme for staff employed at Mid and South"
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 59
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "text": "Essex NHS Foundation Trust"
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 60
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "text": "Refer a Friend Scheme for staff employed at Mid and South Essex NHS Foundation Trust"
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 61
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "At Mid and South Essex NHS Foundation Trust we recognise that you, as our staff, are our most valuable resource. We are proud of the excellent levels of service our Trust provides to our service users and of the dedication of our staff. With this in mind, we feel that our staff are best placed to refer likeminded professionals to join our Trust."
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 62
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "If you know someone; a friend, family member or ex-colleague who shares our culture and values and has the right skills to work with us, then please tell us and we will reward you if your referral is successful."
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 63
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "text": "If your introduction leads to your friend, family member or ex-colleague being appointed to a \u2018hard to fill' role within the Trust either in a substantive or fixed term contract role, you will be entitled to a payment of \u00a3500 once the referred applicant has completed six calendar months of employment within the Trust."
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 64
        },
        {
