        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "text": "To meet the criteria of the scheme and receive your staff referral bonus you must complete and submit the Mid and South Essex NHS Foundation Trust Refer a Friend Scheme Application via a Change Form within 28 days of the referees start date. Forms submitted after this time period may not be valid."
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 71
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "The \u00a3500 will be paid to you (the referrer) at the end of the sixth month of the new employee's employment (in to hard to fill roles only)."
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 72
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "sequence_num": 73,
            "data": {
                "url": "MSEGL-21034 Refer a friend scheme 1.0.005.png"
            }
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "There is no limit to how many claims the referring employee is entitled to claim under the Refer-A- Friend Scheme in any given calendar year."
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 74
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "Referrers must be employed within the Trust to receive payment."
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 75
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "Please note that payments are non-consolidated and will not count towards pension contributions, holiday pay or enhancements. Any payment made will be paid through the Trust payroll and will not subject to appropriate deductions in the normal way."
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 76
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "text": "If you have referred someone to the Refer a Friend scheme and they have been successful appointed to a role the current line manager of the applicant you referred will be required to submit a Contractual Change form to process payment with the understanding of the recruitment cost involved."
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 77
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "This will then be submitted to mse.referafriend@nhs.net"
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 78
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "Example of how to complete the form \u2013 please note you must confirm the full name of the person you have referred, their job title and Trac reference number for the vacancy and their start date."
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 79
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 0,
                "text": "Payment cannot be processed without this information."
            },
            "type": "ListItem",
            "sequence_num": 80
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "sequence_num": 81,
            "data": {
                "url": "MSEGL-21034 Refer a friend scheme 1.0.006.jpeg"
            }
        },
        {
            "data": {
                "is_heading": 1,
                "text": "*All referred staff must have the appropriate UK registered body registration for the referee to qualify for the bonus payment: NMC, GMC etc."
            },
